alternatives.transcript: Welcome to our basic series. These videos have real English for low level beginners. Our teachers teach you words and expressions, you should know. All of these videos are helpful to improve your English, so never give up. It's important to watch these videos and also do some self study. Check any new words you don't understand in a dictionary, and try to always repeat what the teacher says. These videos can be difficult to understand at first, but keep watching. You will get better, you will improve. Let's get started.
